Prerequisites
=============

BTK+ requires the following packages:

 - The GLib, Bango, BdkPixbuf, BATK and bairo libraries, available at the same
   location as BTK+. BTK+ 2.24.33 requires at least GLib 2.28.0,
   Bango 1.20, BdkPixbuf 2.21.0, BATK 1.29.2 and bairo 1.6.0.

 - bobject-introspection 0.9.3 or newer.

Simple install procedure
========================

  % gzip -cd btk+-2.24.33.tar.gz | tar xvf - # unpack the sources
  % cd btk+-2.24.33			   # change to the toplevel directory
  % ./configure				   # run the `configure' script
  % make				   # build BTK+
  [ Become root if necessary ]
  % make install			   # install BTK+

The Details
===========

Complete information about installing BTK+ and related libraries can be found 
in the file:

 docs/reference/btk/html/btk-building.html

Or online at:

 http://developer.bunny.org/doc/API/2.0/btk/btk-building.html

